title: Finding Love in a Gay Bar Ft. Try Guys Zach & Maggie
description:
Dating app etiquette, origin stories, and the behind the scenes of what it's like dating an internet celebrity. Real life couple (and best friends) Zach Kornfeld and Maggie Bustamante make their first IRL appearance on the pod!
